title: Tara Palmer-Tomkinson 'died peacefully in her sleep' | Daily Mail Online
text: Tara Palmer-Tomkinson's family say she 'died peacefully in her sleep' after friends claimed she was struggling with addiction in her final months Tara Palmer-Tomkinson was found dead in her West London flat by her Portuguese cleaner on Wednesday Today her family placed a death notice in a newspaper and said 'Tara Clare died peacefully in her sleep' Comes as a friend appeared on This Morning to claim she had relapsed 'back into a dark place' Sources claimed she had been using cocaine as recently as last year after 'ordering from her dealer' Socialite and model told last year that she had been battling a brain tumour following bombshell diagnosis
